data.description: This tri-level home has 3 bedrooms 2 full baths and 2 car attached garage. Main level features a nice sized foyer leading you to the family room loaded w/windows allowing in the natural sun light & a bedroom. 4 steps up to the upper level features 2 additional bedrooms, kitchen w/plenty of cabinets and storage space, full bath (currently needs finished, seller will leave materials that are at the house for new buyers) The lower level offers an additional full kitchen, living room / rec room area, full bath, storage room, laundry room & sunroom!! Per seller, New roof April 2009, New furnace 3/25/2020, fire place 7/24/2003, New AC 6/10/2005, exterior painted 2023
